      "rationale": "The validation activity directly replicates the COU: the same non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw design, the same ASTM F1717 loading configuration, and the same two-vertebra construct assembly. No extrapolation beyond the validated domain is required for the regulatory submission decision."
