    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted given established regulatory precedent for ASTM F1717 dry ambient testing and the medium model risk classification. Uncertainty quantification via comprehensive Monte Carlo across all inputs confirms that prediction intervals encompass experimental observations for all three QoIs. Overall credibility is sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision.",
